pbs = []
for sam in cell_subset.obs['sample'].unique():
    samp_cell_subset = cell_subset[cell_subset.obs['sample'] == sam]
    #samp_cell_subset.X=samp_cell_subset.layers['counts']
    rep_adata=sc.AnnData(X=samp_cell_subset.X.sum(axis=0), var = samp_cell_subset.var[[]])
    rep_adata.obs_names = [sam]
    rep_adata.obs['type']=samp_cell_subset.obs['type'].iloc[0]  
    pbs.append(rep_adata)
